RT @adultarts: success is not a zero-sum game. one does not have to lose for you to win

5/
As it turns out all it takes is one DM to make dreams come true and the first transgender Metazen was born. I cried at the thought of this internet stranger caring enough to be so inclusive and caring, creating artwork that really spoke to my soul.

4/
I reached out to @MeredithMarsone the artist for Metazens and explained to her that as a trans woman it would be really neat to have my two male Metazens be Metamorphed into a female PFP just like I had dreamed of for myself, morphing into a badass woman.

3/
As it turns out, @MetazensNFT had planned this really neat Metamorph mechanism where you could morph two Metazens to combine into one with shared or new traits. What happened next was really heartwarming and wholesome.

/2
I minted two Metazens when they were in their first iteration and they each turned out to be male PFPs. I was a bit sad that I didn't get a female PFP but I knew I could possibly turn this into an interesting opportunity.
The first project I ever minted was @MetazensNFT so here is a feel good story for you this evening ğŸ¥°
